## My Tech Stack
I am quite adaptive to new tools and "habitats". However, there are some I am sticking to after trying out other alternatives.

### Software I use
#### IDE
I mainly use NVIM with LazyVim plugins after facing memory issues with VSCode for over a year, but if I had to use a GUI based Editor, it would be Zed

#### Testing
I switched to Bruno for API testing as an alternative to Insomnia which itself was an alternative to Postman.
#### Operating System
As every other user, I've always been using Windows- Win10, Win11, but couldn't untill the bloat was too much for my potato laptop.
Then I switched to Linux, specifically Ubuntu, and stayed there for 8 months, after that I jumped to Void Linux.
